==English==

===Alternative spellings===
The "c" in tic, tac, or both may be replaced with a "ck" or with a "t":
*[[tick-tack-toe]]; [[tick-tat-toe]]; [[tit-tat-toe]], etc.
The phrase, or one of the above variations, may be presented without hyphens:
*[[tic tac toe]]; [[tick tat toe]]; [[tit tat toe]], etc.

===Noun===
[[Image:Jogo da velha - tic tac toe.gif|thumb|right|150px|A completed game of tic tac toe, in which the person playing "O" has won.]]
'''tic-tac-toe'''
# a [[game]] in which two [[player]]s put [[circle]]s and [[cross]]es on a 3x3 [[grid]] and try to get three of the same [[symbol]]s in a [[line]]
